ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectEnvironmental Cooperation among the Governments of Canada, the United States of America, and the United Mexican States (ECA) ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT ON ENVIRONMENTAL COOPERATION AMONG THE GOVERNMENTS OF CANADA, THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, AND THE UNITED MEXICAN STATES, done at Mexico City on November 30, 2018, Washington, D.C. on December 11, 2018 and Ottawa on December 18, 2018.
